EM_USO            │  ← bg-primary/10 + text-primary + border\n└───────────────────┘\n\n┌───────────────────┐\n│ MANUTENCAO        │  ← bg-amber-500/10 + text-amber-400 + border\n└───────────────────┘\n```\n\n### Button States\n```\nDefault (Primary):\n  Idle:    bg-primary text-white\n  Hover:   bg-primary/90 (mais escuro)\n  Click:   scale-95 (feedback)\n  Focus:   ring-1 ring-primary\n\nOutline:\n  Idle:    border-zinc-700/50 bg-background\n  Hover:   bg-zinc-900/50 border-zinc-600/50\n  Click:   scale-95\n\nGhost:\n  Idle:    transparent text-zinc-400\n  Hover:   bg-zinc-900/50 text-zinc-200\n  Click:   scale-95\n\nDestructive:\n  Idle:    bg-red-500/10 text-red-400 border-red-500/20\n  Hover:   bg-red-500/20\n  Click:   scale-95\n```\n\n---\n\n## ⚡ Transições e Animações\n\n### Standard Transitions\n```\nHover States:\n  duration-200\n  transition-all / transition-colors / transition-opacity\n\nExample:\n  hover:bg-zinc-800/30 transition-colors duration-200\n\nModal Animations:\n  Modal: animate-in zoom-in-95 duration-300\n  Backdrop: animate-in fade-in duration-300\n\nProgress Bars:\n  duration-500 (mais lento para visual smooth)\n\nScale Feedback:\n  active:scale-95 (click feedback)\n\nOpacity Reveal:\n  opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📱 Responsiveness Breakpoints\n\n### Mobile (< 640px)\n```\nTopbar:\n  h-14 (reduzido)\n  px-4 (padding reduzido)\n  Search: max-w-xs\n  User info: hidden\n\nDashboard:\n  Grid: grid-cols-2 (2 stat cards por linha)\n  Text: text-xs (smaller)\n  Padding: p-4\n\nTable:\n  Colunas ocultas: type, setor, criticidade\n  Icons: h-4 w-4\n  Actions: h-7 w-7\n  Responsive layout\n\nSidebar:\n  Colapsável obrigatoriamente em mobile\n  Width: w-16 (apenas ícones)\n```\n\n### Tablet (640px - 1024px)\n```\nDashboard:\n  Grid: grid-cols-3 (3 stat cards)\n  Text: text-sm\n  Padding: p-6\n\nTable:\n  Mostrar: type, setor\n  Ocultar: criticidade\n\nSidebar:\n  Colapsável opcionalmente\n  Width: w-64 (com labels)\n\nForm:\n  Grid: grid-cols-2 (2 inputs por linha)\n```\n\n### Desktop (> 1024px)\n```\nDashboard:\n  Grid: grid-cols-4 (4 stat cards)\n  Secundário: grid-cols-7 (4 + 3)\n  Text: text-sm / text-base\n  Padding: p-8\n\nTable:\n  Mostrar: todos as colunas\n  Full responsive\n\nSidebar:\n  Sempre visível\n  Width: w-64\n  Não colapsável por padrão\n\nForm:\n  Grid: grid-cols-2\n  max-w-lg modal\n```\n\n---\n\n## ✨ Premium Touches\n\n### Subtle Effects\n- **Backdrop Blur**: Modais e topbar\n- **Color Opacity**: /10, /20, /30, /50 para refinamento\n- **Shadow**: shadow-sm (leve) ao invés de pesada\n- **Border Opacity**: border-zinc-800/50 para suavidade\n\n### Micro-interactions\n- **Hover**: Sempre presente, suave, contextual\n- **Focus**: Ring sutil com cor primary\n- **Active**: Scale 95% para feedback\n- **Disabled**: Opacidade 50%, sem cursor\n\n### Typography\n- **Labels**: UPPERCASE, font-semibold, tracking-wide (premium feel)\n- **Titles**: font-bold, tracking-tight (control)\n- **Body**: font-normal, clear hierarchy\n- **Secondary**: text-zinc-500/600 (discreta)\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 Checklist Visual\n\nAo adicionar nova feature, verificar:\n\n- [ ] Labels em uppercase com tracking-wide\n- [ ] Inputs rounded-lg com border-zinc-700/50\n- [ ] Focus states com ring-primary/30\n- [ ] Hover states em tudo interativo\n- [ ] Transições 200ms smooth\n- [ ] Spacing: gap-4 ou space-y-4\n- [ ] Padding: p-5 sm:p-6\n- [ ] Borders: border-zinc-800/50\n- [ ] Text colors: zinc-{300,400,500}\n- [ ] Responsive: sm:, md:, lg:\n- [ ] Icons: h-4 w-4 ou h-5 w-5 (not bigger!)\n- [ ] Badges: com borders e backgrounds suaves\n\n---\n\n## 📚 Referência Rápida\n\n### Cores Principais\n```\nBackground:    bg-zinc-950 ou bg-zinc-900\nCard:          bg-card (zinc-900)\nBorder:        border-zinc-800/50\nText Primary:  text-zinc-100 ou text-zinc-200\nText Secondary: text-zinc-400 ou text-zinc-500\nHover:         bg-zinc-800/50 ou hover:text-zinc-200\n```\n\n### Spacing\n```\nSmall:  p-2, gap-1.5, space-y-2\nMedium: p-4, gap-3, space-y-4\nLarge:  p-6, gap-4, space-y-6\n```\n\n### Typography\n```\nH1: text-3xl font-bold\nH2: text-2xl font-bold  \nH3: text-base font-semibold\nBody: text-sm font-normal\nSmall: text-xs font-medium\nLabel: text-xs font-semibold uppercase\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🎓 Premium Principles\n\n1. **Less is More** - Espaço em branco é seu amigo\n2. **Subtle Interactions** - Nada exagerado\n3. **Consistent Spacing** - Múltiplos de 4px\n4. **Clear Hierarchy** - Tipo e peso bem definidos\n5. **Thoughtful Colors** - Propósito em cada cor\n6. **Smooth Transitions** - 200ms é o padrão\n7. **Responsive Everything** - Mobile-first sempre\n8. **Accessible Design** - Contraste e keyboard nav\n\n---\n\n**NovaPrata Labs: Built for Premium Experience** ✨\n"
